arts.ttl: Messiâ€™s last-second assist lifts Inter Miami over Atlas 2-1 in Leagues Cup
arts.sum: Lionel Messi had two assists, including one in the final seconds of the match, to help lift Inter Miami over Atlas 2-1 in their Leagues Cup opener on Wednesday night. That meant five assists in July for Messi, who was named the Major League Soccer Player of the Month after netting eight goals and helping Miami go 4-1-1 in league play.

arts.ttl: Availability update: Is De Paul eligible for Inter Miami's clash with Atlas?
arts.sum: The MLS reveal whether Inter Miami's Rodrigo De Paul is eligible to make his debut in Wednesday's Leagues Cup match against Atlas.
